Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:42.51,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決 斷 之 時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西也很厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐大人 有客人找您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？哦 讓他過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐「大人」？ 真臭屁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然隨便打開我的貨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候變成得這麼了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是我讓他們這麼幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瓦隆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「將這個地球打造成我等的理想鄉」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第二個阿瓦隆」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「別猶豫」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾絲在加爾剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和艾米在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長話短說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘艦團的人到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人都像幽靈一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼神都像被附身了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我船上的居民肯定也會被變成那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是如此 我當初離開加爾剛蒂亞又有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就甘願這樣下去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人正在打算謀反
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是來接我的衝浪龍蝦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海賊拉凱奇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那就跟那個龍蝦合作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙想指望破廢鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過雷德那傢伙不會幫忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就得這樣過一輩子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「把帆布展開來收集雨水」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你濕透了呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「會感冒的哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:05:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以前觀測到的稱為「雨」的氣像現象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未感知到特殊異常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神賜予了我們巨大的恩典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們將前往神的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獻上至高的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為生者而死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你們要做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為救贖人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而永垂不朽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些是人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不是為了看這些…而來到這裡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個瘋狂的艦團接下來將駛向加爾剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙我果然受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了從希迪亞斯手中保護大家才來到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護艾米 為了保護貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護那些人們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫蓋爾中校發令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「雷德少尉進入臨戰態勢」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「聽從我的指揮」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請貴官進行判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判斷嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我判斷 你執行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我或許從未真正做出過選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解貴官的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校的指令…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 你和Striker的戰力差有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數據不足 無法計算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解貴官的提問意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能夠和Striker戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Striker X3752目前的行為不屬於同盟的軍務範疇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以認定為交戰對象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我能和中校戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對該問題的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已超出本機作為駕駛員支援啟發系統的機能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在任何情況下 戰鬥方針的制定均交由貴官判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 使用無線會被攔截
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能直接傳達給他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這麼重大的使命 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能飛往加爾剛蒂亞的只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你 拯救大家吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你可欠我一個人情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 進入臨戰態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾…剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾剛蒂亞…要被襲擊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人開著衝浪風箏飛過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗雅 艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保護加爾剛蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能聽梅露蒂的 改變航路進行避難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的立場 不得不這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德讓我們逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算自己去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算代替我們 一個人去戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為了保護加爾剛蒂亞 甚至不惜和過去的同伴反目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我們卻要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然他作出了選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也必須作出選擇才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧爾德姆醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特 該是使用那把鑰匙的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天梯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身負艦團賢者之任的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依據職責建議艦團長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是使用之時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 希望你也能助我們一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為讓世界領略我偉大的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領略偉大的神力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣佈 新的聖戰就此打響
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將會得到勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為給這個星球帶來絕對的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為將這個星球建設成安寧華貴的理想鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順從於我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是通往恆久幸福的唯一道路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德少尉 這玩笑可不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是同盟戰士該有的發言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是銀河同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是人類居住的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的未來是我們的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,責任？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這顆星球上有著活在這裡的人們所建立的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有理由破壞它！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我等的正義不變」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「別猶豫」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 這是神之間的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力怎麼會這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測其威力並非來源於內部發生器 而來源於外部裝備的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保存自身能量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 給這顆星球帶來新的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐 你快撤 這是我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你們也不怎麼討人喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個裝神弄鬼的玩意更讓人不爽一萬倍！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一發 準備好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不參戰的普通居民在裝甲區域內躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備救生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本船是本艦團的母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能成為攻擊目標 請做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能饒恕叛亂 反抗的全都是敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我就是這麼粗魯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你還挺男人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你另眼相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我踹開他們過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以在戰略上確保有利地位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建議採取打即跑戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.98,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(724,650)}Hit-and-run Tactics
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中攻擊敵機頭部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想殺死中校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機的機動性凌駕於本機之上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「無論強者還是弱者」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「均依靠自身的理性相互扶持」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這才能稱為人類吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不是嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我打中！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生器 以最大功率輸出！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我說 雷德」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「願不願意與我一起改變這個星球？」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始接近敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸入緊急開倉信號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「還好有你在」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 還願意 跟隨我…嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姿勢控制系統 重啟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德少尉 貴官的抵抗是毫無意義的
